      <title>贪吃蛇</title>
      <link href="/2023/12/19/%E8%B4%AA%E5%90%83%E8%9B%87/"/>
      <url>/2023/12/19/%E8%B4%AA%E5%90%83%E8%9B%87/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="关于单杀学校布置的小组作业-贪吃蛇"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#关于单杀学校布置的小组作业-贪吃蛇"></a> 关于<s>单杀</s>学校布置的小组作业 —— 贪吃蛇</h2><h3 id="功能构想"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#功能构想"></a> 功能构想</h3><ul><li>正常的操作贪吃蛇具有的吃食物、增加长度、碰撞死亡、展示分数</li><li>具有可重复游玩功能<ul><li>死亡后可选择退出或重开</li><li>暂停后可选择退出或重开</li></ul></li><li>具有可暂停功能</li><li>中途可强制退出</li><li>可随时自主调整速度 / 可在游戏开始前自主选择难度（二选一）</li><li>具有积分排行榜</li><li>具有双人对战模式</li><li>具有主菜单界面（选做）</li><li>伪AI人机对战 <s>（这够离谱）</s></li></ul><p>目前未实现:</p><blockquote><p><s>可在游戏开始前自主选择难度</s>(现在修改为游戏内自主调整速度)</p></blockquote><blockquote><p><s>具有积分排行榜</s>(不打算做了)</p></blockquote><h3 id="实现思路"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#实现思路"></a> 实现思路</h3><h4 id="一-正常的贪吃蛇具有的吃食物-增加长度-碰撞死亡-展示分数"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#一-正常的贪吃蛇具有的吃食物-增加长度-碰撞死亡-展示分数"></a> 一、正常的贪吃蛇具有的吃食物、增加长度、碰撞死亡、展示分数</h4><blockquote><p>首先，进行蛇的构造</p></blockquote><p>这里使用使用双向链表构建，包括：</p><ol><li>蛇的节点的构造<ol><li>坐标</li><li>指向下一个节点、上一个节点的指针</li></ol></li><li>蛇的构造<ol><li>指向蛇头、蛇尾的指针（为了方便进行特殊操作如吃食物、碰撞判断、节点增加）</li><li>蛇头方向</li><li>节点数量</li></ol></li></ol><p>值得注意的是：蛇的构造中的指针指向蛇的节点，这样可以较为简单地进行操作</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Node</span>&#123;    <span class="comment">//构造蛇节点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> X;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> Y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Node</span>* Next;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Node</span>* Pre;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Node* LinkNode;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Snake</span>&#123;   <span class="comment">//构造蛇</span></span><br><span class="line">    LinkNode Head;</span><br><span class="line">    LinkNode Tail;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> Direction;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> Num;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Snake snake1, snake2;   <span class="comment">//snake1, snake2是为了双人模式准备的</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>其次，进行食物的构造</p></blockquote><p>这里使用结构体直接构造即可：</p><ol><li>坐标</li><li>是否存在（避免食物的重复生成）</li></ol><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title class_">Food</span>&#123;    <span class="comment">//食物构造</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> X;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> Y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">bool</span> Exist;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Food food1, food2;  <span class="comment">//用food1, food2同样是为了双人模式</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>然后，进行蛇的死亡判定（这里只写判定判定判定，还没到死亡后的代码）</p></blockquote><p>有且仅有两种死亡方式：</p><ol><li>碰到墙体</li><li>碰到自己</li></ol><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//碰到墙体</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> collidewall1 = snake1.Head-&gt;X &gt; MAX_X || snake1.Head-&gt;Y &gt; MAX_Y || snake1.Head-&gt;X &lt; MIN_X || snake1.Head-&gt;Y &lt; MIN_Y;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//一个语句就可以实现的就没必要再用函数了（函数已经够多了）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title">CollideSnake</span><span class="params">(Snake snake)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(snake.Num &lt; <span class="number">3</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">//在传统贪吃蛇游戏里节点数小于3不可能发生自我碰撞</span></span><br><span class="line">    LinkNode node = snake.Head-&gt;Next;   <span class="comment">//头不可能与头发生碰撞</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(node != snake.Tail-&gt;Next)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(node-&gt;X == snake.Head-&gt;X &amp;&amp; node-&gt;Y == snake.Head-&gt;Y)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        node = node-&gt;Next;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;   <span class="comment">//这么走了一圈还没检测到自然就没发生碰撞</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>然后，蛇蛇该动起来啦</p></blockquote><p>其实蛇的移动的规律就是复制前一个点的位置移动，所以说到底，就是复制蛇头的移动</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title">SnakeBodyMove</span><span class="params">(Snake&amp; snake)</span>    <span class="comment">//因为每个节点的位置坐标会改变，所以这里传地址</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    LinkNode linknode = snake.Tail; <span class="comment">//从蛇尾开始复制前一个节点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(linknode != snake.Head)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        linknode-&gt;X = linknode-&gt;Pre-&gt;X;</span><br><span class="line">        linknode-&gt;Y = linknode-&gt;Pre-&gt;Y;</span><br><span class="line">        linknode = linknode-&gt;Pre;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从尾节点开始一步一步复制前一个节点直到头节点</p><p>至于如何控制蛇的方向，，，当然是用键盘输入呀！ヾ(•ω•`)o这难道还要贴代码？</p><blockquote><p>食物生成</p></blockquote><p>这个挺简单的，判断食物存不存在然后取随机数</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (!food1.Exist)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> x;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">int</span> y;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">srand</span>(<span class="built_in">time</span>(<span class="number">0</span>));</span><br><span class="line">x = (<span class="built_in">rand</span>() % <span class="number">54</span>) * <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line">y = (<span class="built_in">rand</span>() % <span class="number">36</span>) * <span class="number">20</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">LinkNode linknode = snake1.Head;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> cont = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (linknode != snake1.Tail-&gt;Next)   <span class="comment">//需要注意的是食物不能生成在蛇身上</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (linknode-&gt;X == x &amp;&amp; linknode-&gt;Y == y)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">cont = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">linknode = linknode-&gt;Next;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (cont)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">food1.X = x;</span><br><span class="line">food1.Y = y;</span><br><span class="line">food1.Exist = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">DrawFood</span>(food1);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>吃食物并且增加节点</p></blockquote><p>吃食物很简单：食物的坐标与蛇头的坐标重合就算吃到了</p><p>关键是增加节点——只需要用一个空节点，然后将它接在蛇的链表表尾就可以了</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (snake1.Head-&gt;X == food1.X &amp;&amp; snake1.Head-&gt;Y == food1.Y &amp;&amp; food1.Exist)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">food1.Exist = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">G_Score1 += <span class="number">10</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">LinkNode nodes = (LinkNode)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(<span class="built_in">sizeof</span>(Node));    <span class="comment">//定义空节点</span></span><br><span class="line">nodes-&gt;X = ends.X;</span><br><span class="line">nodes-&gt;Y = ends.Y;</span><br><span class="line">nodes-&gt;Next = snake1.Tail-&gt;Next;</span><br><span class="line">nodes-&gt;Pre = snake1.Tail;</span><br><span class="line">snake1.Tail-&gt;Next = nodes;  <span class="comment">//连接空节点</span></span><br><span class="line">snake1.Tail = nodes;    <span class="comment">//更新尾部指针指向</span></span><br><span class="line">++snake1.Num;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">DrawSnakeNode</span>(ends);    <span class="comment">//画出尾节点</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">ClearDisplay</span>(); <span class="comment">//清除展示区信息</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">DrawScore</span>();    <span class="comment">//打印分数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">DrawNodes</span>();    <span class="comment">//打印蛇长</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">DrawSpeed</span>();    <span class="comment">//打印速度</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>展示分数</p></blockquote><p>没什么好说的，用<s>Not</s>EasyX直接画就行了，这里就不贴代码了</p><h4 id="二-双人对战和人机对战"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#二-双人对战和人机对战"></a> 二、双人对战和人机对战</h4><blockquote><p>双人对战</p></blockquote><p>实现方法巨简单，只需要从单人模式里copy再粘一份改参数就可以了</p><p>唯一麻烦的是游戏场景要重新用<s>Not</s>EasyX画，这是整个代码第二折磨我的地方</p><p>(什么？你问我第一折磨是什么？当然是<s>摸鱼导致什么都没写啊</s>DeBug啊！)</p><blockquote><p>人机对战</p></blockquote><p>我最喜欢的一部分了，所以……</p><p><s>下次再继续写</s></p>]]></content>
      
      
